  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Glidescope and chest CT iminge for the placement of the Univent Tube Without Fiberoptic
      Bronchoscope Assistance
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Comparing the traditional method of Univent Tube intubation and Glidescope combined with
      chest CT iminge guide the precise localization of double lumen endotracheal tube
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
